  "content": "e-label\">The Root Cause</div>\n  <div class=\"slide-title\">\n    A Designer Who<br>\n    <span class=\"highlight-purple\">Can't Look Up</span><br>\n    From the Code\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"slide-subtitle\">\n    The gap isn't intelligence. It's perception.\n  </div>\n  <div style=\"display: flex; gap: 32px; margin-bottom: 28px;\">\n    <div style=\"flex: 1; text-align: center;\">\n      <div style=\"font-size: 56px; margin-bottom: 16px;\">&#128104;&#8205;&#128187;</div>\n      <h3 style=\"font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 16px;\">Human Designer</h3>\n      <div style=\"display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 14px;\">\n        <div style=\"background: rgba(59,130,246,0.15); border: 1px solid rgba(59,130,246,0.3); border-radius: 12px; padding: 16px 28px; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 600; width: 90%;\">Write CSS</div>\n        <div style=\"font-size: 28px; color: var(--accent-green);\">&#8595;</div>\n        <div style=\"background: rgba(16,185,129,0.15); border: 1px solid rgba(16,185,129,0.3); border-radius: 12px; padding: 16px 28px; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; width: 90%;\">Look at browser</div>\n        <div style=\"font-size: 28px; color: var(--accent-green);\">&#8595;</div>\n        <div style=\"background: rgba(245,158,11,0.15); border: 1px solid rgba(245,158,11,0.3); border-radius: 12px; padding: 16px 28px; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 600; width: 90%;\">Adjust</div>\n        <div style=\"font-size: 28px; color: var(--accent-green);\">&#8635;</div>\n        <div style=\"font-size: 24px; color: var(--accent-green); font-weight: 600;\">Feedback loop</div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; font-size: 48px; color: var(--text-muted);\">vs</div>",
